\displaystyle E(g(M))=\int_0^1\int_0^1g(y_1-y_2)1_{\{y_1>y_2\}}dy_1dy_2=\int_0^{1}\int_{y_2}^1g(y_1-y_2)dy_1dy_2
M=|X_1-X_2|
E(g(M))
(u,v)=(y-x,x)
